</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="12">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$hao-le-19-52" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/hao-le-19-52" class="zg-link" title="[已重置]">[已重置]</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-ling-xi-4" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-ling-xi-4" class="zg-link" title="李泠西">李泠西</a></span>
